{"tid":1486161,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[網絡行動] 一齊收垃圾藍屍content farm channel皮","createTime":"2019-08-18T19:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T13:16:11.000Z","uid":126889,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"568f13a5ec5ed85d387c7148c484fd0adbc8d27f","tid":1486161,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:09:20.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩想上網搵下上禮拜眼中槍女義士既新聞<br />\n睇新聞既話，近排除左上連登都睇下youtube d人點評論，走出一下個同溫層<br />\n<br />\n竟然比我搵到一條咁既片<br />\n<strong>- 811女暴徒被射盲眼真相 - </strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2GgrOO7NBpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2GgrOO7NBpg&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=d9a4e0fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2GgrOO7NBpg</a><br />\n<br />\n我真係即時屌又出黎，人地盲左已經慘仲要咁樣老屈返女醫護係暴徒<br />\n再睇睇下，你老母，有成38萬 VIEWS<br />\n睇落去原來係個傻閪何志光既CHANNEL，有成10萬訂閱<br />\n平均佢一條片都有數以萬計既點擊<br />\n<br />\n佢既channel 我相信係中共既大外宣統戰下既冰山一角，係依家大家都急不及待咁檢討<del>(互屌)</del>今日戰果時，其實網絡上既輿論好多戰線都失守緊。<br />\n成件事好唔樂觀，因為大量假資訊流通緊，而竟然好多人都未注意到。<br />\n唔單止片，仲有好多網軍五毛係度留言。<br />\n開依個POST，當然想大家即刻去report佢之外，真心希望大家真係少上連登，接觸/觀察/反制唔同平台。<br />\n依家難得外國開始陸續支持香港，冇理由比大陸d 假消息打低架，仲未知佢地會唔會賤到自導自演d 故仔出黎。<br />\n睇到垃圾大陸fake news/ 五毛既巴打，不仿用多幾秒時間report，莫以善小而不為。<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bdd88f3591d6e75b431cbbc0dded83c94ad17be","tid":1486161,"uid":241458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:15:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有人諗住聽朝0715塞鐵，好可能會spin走咗車長罷工嘅事，希望深水埗手足聽朝去勸下佢地<br />\n<br />\n佢地個group block咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mtrisdangerous\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtrisdangerous&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=75608b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/mtrisdangerous</a>"},{"pid":"7a5e084b604d60c873f362a3d2881a57f42d7ba3","tid":1486161,"uid":301266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:30:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b294ff72621b0b2a1610b54d338b89258921dca","tid":1486161,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:37:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48e9ff34ffe6f7bfd4d5731f5a00760a0c664995","tid":1486161,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bdd88f3591d6e75b431cbbc0dded83c94ad17be","tid":1486161,"uid":241458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:15:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">緊急</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有人諗住聽朝0715塞鐵，好可能會spin走咗車長罷工嘅事，希望深水埗手足聽朝去勸下佢地<br />\n<br />\n佢地個group block咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/mtrisdangerous\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmtrisdangerous&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsgPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=75608b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/mtrisdangerous</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:39:06.000Z","msg":"塞鐵係香港個context 底下吃力不討好<br />\n但你話全民跳閘可能人會易D支持"},{"pid":"aa8e19b32f8acf27393d10d415a71475925b6c18","tid":1486161,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:40:13.000Z","msg":"借推<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇留意，今日8點幾9點嘅時候，夏愨道D車係一堆咁連續駛入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486112\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486112</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f8727e8c0a4e7694951b652dce445bdcb8191669","tid":1486161,"uid":242444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:42:42.000Z","msg":"越睇越嬲"},{"pid":"8e5a1410536c1edea6aad292a3d6f14ce4ded648","tid":1486161,"uid":126889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T19:51:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dddd63c96dd80a1c1157cc70ccaec13184f033a","